A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 PFAS Chemicals – Civil Actions and Prohibition on Consumer Product Sales
3 FOR the purpose of altering certain time limits for bringing certain civil actions concerning
4 exposure of a person to PFAS chemicals; prohibiting a person, on or after a certain
5 date, from manufacturing, selling, or distributing in the State a certain consumer
6 product that contains PFAS chemicals; and generally relating to PFAS chemicals.
